title: Deposit fees
body:
Proposal to have deposit fees in all pools and the fees generated will be subjected to burning. This will increase the value of holding BREW since it has deposit fees. 

Also the farming pools can have durations say 2 weeks then it is reset to start new farming pools. 

More interaction, the more bnb fees generated and it could bring CafeSwap to top projects in BUIDL program.
